[h2 id=HelloTASvideos,it'sbeenawhileagain! 
	"Hello TASvideos, it's been a while again!
	$LF
]h2
[h3 id=Aboutmyrun 
	"About my run
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"This is my story about fighting against the game's laws and psychics.
	$LF
	"i want to tell you clearly things that i did and didn't do.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"When i started this project i wasn't sure how much it can be improved and what 
	$LF
	"different problems, things i am going to face in my journey. I was really amazed 
	$LF
	"after starting this project how you can detect certain lag points by sliding, charging,
	$LF
	"even pressing right,down while sliding sometimes.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"I think some of you are wondering and so on why my re-record
	$LF
	"count is so high but there's a clear explanation for it.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"- I am calm but stubborn person in a certain ways because i love to overdue my projects with great amount of caution. When i faced problems with this game, i got really excited
	$LF
	"and i tried to use every button-combos even weird ones that came to my mind to see if i can find something 
	$LF
	"unexpected that helps. This way worked the most but it caused a lot of extra work and re-records.
	$LF
	"I can't say any other reason for my different way of working.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Aboutthegame 
	"About the game
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"This game may look really simple and easy but that thought isn't correct
	$LF
	"its hard, laggy, feed out of bugs, filled of randomness kind of game.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Laws 
	"Laws
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"Sub-pixel position isn't a big problem actually you don't need to worry about
	$LF
	"it so much expect if you face 1-2 frame of lag-points but they can be simply avoided by pressing A
	$LF
	"near of the edge or charging your weapon. If i had problems where i lost frame or two i simple stopped sliding somewhere
	$LF
	"and repeated that until i get the right or faster frame to land.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"For the bosses i entered the door in different position or in a different frame to get good distance.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Goals 
