[h3 id=Specialinformationaboutthestagesandwork 
	"Special information about the stages and work
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"I found improvements from the each stage but they were yet insanely hard to find.
	$LF
]div
[pre 
	$LF
]pre
[div class=p 
	"I tried to change the game route example. start with the windman stage first and use 
	$LF
	"buster in the boss fight, for some reason sliding, charging was much slower if compared to 
	$LF
	"Flameman fight.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Flameman 
	" Flameman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"One of the stages that haves much lag and randomness, i tried to solve myself
	$LF
	"out from that puzzle. Later i realized that you can reduce lag by sliding (or charge your buster faster)
	$LF
	"this technique worked best in the Flameman fight for some reason.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"AngerFist thought a little faster way to the third screen, but 
	$LF
	"randomness forced me to gain only "2 frames" for a while and after that everything was lost and much more.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Blizzardman 
	" Blizzardman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Simple stage with a high load of lag, i realized how to use flameman's weapon to minimize lag better
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Plantman 
	" Plantman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Well.. one of the stages that caused me to take a little break because there was many ways to improve things
	$LF
	"and i need to test them all out. For the boss i found a good way to less lag.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Tomahawkman 
	" Tomahawkman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"I decicated to use Buster instead of Flame weapon because it wasn't so slow as it looks 
	$LF
	"and it handled the lag much more better and smoother in the end.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Yamatoman 
	" Yamatoman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Nothing special, tried to fight against lag that flying enemies made a lot.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Knightman 
	" Knightman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"This was a weird stage, i won or lost frames there and there and i need to do that level couple of
	$LF
	"times to see what is the fastest way to beat the level.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Centaurman 
	" Centaurman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"I found out that you change the gameway bit and you were able slip below the pelican and continue your sliding.
	$LF
	"I took damage instead of waiting charging buster in the room with two mine enemies.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Windman 
	" Windman
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"In the fifth screen i didn't take damage and i used a bit different route because 
	$LF
	"it changed the gameway a bit later so i was able to skip lag-points.
	$LF
	"I also realized that its better to walk/jump near of the moving enemies to detect lag.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Mr.XStage1 
	" Mr. X Stage 1
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"I didn't expect to find any improvements from the stage but i tried to change weapon in a different
	$LF
	"time and jump lower or higher while using megajet.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Mr.XStage2 
	" Mr. X Stage 2
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Didn't expect to see improvements here but i had good luck and i found a few little things out
	$LF
	"that can help you to go forward.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Mr.XStage3 
	" Mr. X Stage 3
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
