	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Dr.WilyStage1 
	" Dr. Wily Stage 1
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"I changed weapon straight way to yamatoman's weapon instead of buster and then to yamato again. 
	$LF
	"Weapon changes takes much time to do so i was curious and it was a good idea in the end.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"For the boss i found the key route so i was able to get that elevator to spawn
	$LF
	"so fast as possible and shoot every time as possible.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Dr.WilyStage2 
	" Dr. Wily Stage 2
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Only got few frames from the stage and they come from the enemies that are in the end of the stage.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Dr.WilyStage3 
	" Dr. Wily Stage 3
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Found a technique that saves a lot of time in the boss re-fights. I Changed my weapon after i defeated
	$LF
	"the boss because i realized that it tooks much more time to change your weapon outside of the bossroom expect between Centaurman and Windman because it appeared to be 30-40 frames slower.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Dr.WilyStage4 
	" Dr. Wily Stage 4
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	""i came from the base and i aim to the wily's base." I found a good way to hit huge machine wily
	$LF
	"5 frames faster while trying to hit second time.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"I manipulated flying wily to the right upper corner to shoot from more far away to "shoot earlier."
	$LF
]div
